     1→# mdbook-compare
     3→This is a simple utility to compare the output of two different versions of mdbook.
     4→
     5→To use this:
     6→
     7→1. Install [`tidy`](https://www.html-tidy.org/).
     8→2. Install or build the initial version of mdbook that you want to compare.
     9→3. Install or build the new version of mdbook that you want to compare.
    10→4. Run `mdbook-compare` with the arguments to the mdbook executables and the books to build.
